--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.3.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 0.2.1 (2019-03-11)
E: Execute 'update' before counting packages (resynchronize package index files)
E: Use 'dist-upgrade' instead of 'upgrade' command

* Version 0.2.0 (2019-03-08)
F: Add 'apt_check-update' script

* Version 0.1.0 (2019-03-05)
F: Initial release
